gloss_en: I like it. / I don't like it.

item.targetText: 저는 그게 좋아요./저는 그게 좋아하지 않아요.

gloss_en: I'm free today. / I'm not free today.
This is okay. / Is this okay?
You have time. / Do you have time?
This is yours. / Is this yours?
I have it./I don't have it.

item.targetText: 저는 그걸 가지고 있어요./저는 그걸 가지고 있지 않아요.

gloss_en: I need it./I don't need it.
You need help./Do you need help?
I bought it at the store.
I left it in the room.
Let's meet in front of the station.
There is a problem./There is no problem.
I have time./I don't have time.
There is a seat./There is no seat.
I have a question./I have no questions.
I have cash./I don't have cash.
There is a solution./There is no solution.
I want to go, but I can't.
It's close, but hard to find.
I'm busy, but I can help.
I understand, but I'm not sure.
If you have time, tell me.
If you need help, call me.
If it's not busy, let's talk.
If it rains, I won't go.
Is it okay to take a photo?
Is it okay if I join?

item.targetText: 한 번 더 말해 주실 수 있나요?

gloss_en: If you don't mind, could you help?
Where can I charge my phone?
Is it okay if I sit?
Is it okay to change it?
I don't think it's a good idea.

item.targetText: 그 얘긴 들어 본 적 없어요.
이 앱은 써 본 적 없어요.

gloss_en: Not yet, I'm still working on it.

item.targetText: 다시 한 번 말씀해 주실 수 있어요?
천천히 다시 말해 주실 수 있어요?

gloss_en: Could you send it to me?

item.targetText: 창문 좀 열어 주실 수 있어요?
조금 더 크게 말해 주실 수 있어요?

gloss_en: Could you show me where it is?

item.targetText: 어디 있는지 알려 주실 수 있어요?

gloss_en: Could you give me an example?
Could you keep it a secret?
Could you email me the details?

item.targetText: 자세한 내용 이메일로 보내 주실 수 있어요?
볼륨 좀 낮춰 주실 수 있어요?

gloss_en: Could you hold this for a second?

item.targetText: 이거 잠깐 들어 주실 수 있어요?

gloss_en: Could you message me when you arrive?
If you have time, could you help me?
If it's okay, could you send it?
When you get a chance, please reply.

item.targetText: 혹시 이거 확인해 줄 수 있어요?

gloss_en: Sorry to bother you, but could you help?
If you don't mind, could you translate this?

item.targetText: 괜찮으시면 이거 번역해 줄 수 있어요?

gloss_en: Could you do me a quick favor?
If possible, could you move it up?

item.targetText: 가능하면 좀 앞당겨 줄 수 있어요?

gloss_en: Would it be okay if I asked a question?
If you have a minute, could you call me?

item.targetText: 잠깐 시간 되면 전화해 줄 수 있어요?

gloss_en: If it's not too much trouble, could you check it?
If you can, please send it today.
Could you possibly explain it one more time?

item.targetText: 가능하면 한 번 더 설명해 줄 수 있어요?

gloss_en: If you don't mind, could we change the plan?
If you're okay with it, could you join us?
Could you maybe send me the link?

item.targetText: 혹시 링크 보내 줄 수 있어요?

gloss_en: If it's convenient, could we meet earlier?

item.targetText: 괜찮으면 좀 더 일찍 만날 수 있어요?

gloss_en: If you can, please remind me.

item.targetText: 가능하면 다시 보내 줄 수 있어요?

gloss_en: If you're not busy, could you talk?

item.targetText: 안 바쁘면 잠깐 이야기할 수 있어요?

gloss_en: If it's okay, could you keep the door open?

item.targetText: 괜찮으면 문을 열어 둬 줄 수 있어요?

gloss_en: Could you maybe lower your voice?

item.targetText: 혹시 목소리 좀 낮춰 줄 수 있어요?

gloss_en: If you can, please let me know.
If it's fine, could I ask for your opinion?
If possible, could you send it by tomorrow?

item.targetText: 가능하면 내일까지 보내 줄 수 있어요?

gloss_en: If you want, you can say no.
If you don't mind, could you share it?
When you have time, could you review it?

item.targetText: 시간 될 때 봐 줄 수 있어요?

gloss_en: If it's okay, could we talk later?
I'll check and let you know.

item.targetText: 한 번 가 본 적 있어요.

gloss_en: Have you ever used this app?

item.targetText: 이 앱 써 본 적 있어요?
